commands.EMBEDIMAGES: Embeds raster images from XREFs into the drawing by converting them to OLE objects using PowerPoint, preserving orientation.
commands.EMBEDPDFS: Embeds PDF underlays into the drawing by converting them to PNG and then OLE objects using PowerPoint.
commands.CLEANTBLK: Cleans the title block by exploding blocks, keeping only the title block, detaching XREFs, and embedding images.
commands.CLEANCAD: Cleans the entire sheet by embedding XREFs and performing cleanup operations.
commands.DETACHSIGX: Detaches signature/logo/stamp style XREFs and related special references.
commands.WALLSONLY: Keeps wall objects and turns off non-wall layers in model space.
